OL,5, Car makers have expressed dismay over  
OL,6, plans to make electric cars subject to 
OL,7, vehicle excise duty, in line with      
OL,8, petrol, diesel and hybrid vehicles.    
OL,10,FThe tax will apply from April 2025, the
OL,11,Fchancellor said in his Autumn          
OL,12,FStatement.                             
OL,14,FNissan, which makes several electric   
OL,15,Fmodels, said it was concerned about the
OL,16,Fpotential impact on sales of the new   
OL,17,Ftax.                                   
OL,19,FTim Slatter, the UK chairman of Ford,  
OL,20,Fdescribed the move as "short-sighted". 
